creator: Epignosis UK LTD
descriptionHtml:
DFS University e-CAMPUS mobile is the perfect companion for delivering learning right at your fingertips.
The mobile-app does not try to be everything that the web-app is but offers ample opportunities for delivering rich, mobile optimized courses.

With the e-CAMPUS, learners can:

- Access assigned courses and train anywhere, anytime
- Resume any in progress courses that they started on desktop
- View progress, and gamification elements like points, levels and badges
- Download courses for offline usage and synchronize when online

The e-CAMPUS is built upon an award-winning learning management system that allows you to deliver great learning courses to employees, partners, customers or students with ease.
descriptionShort: Mobile learning app for DFS employees

London W14 8TH,
United Kingdom
appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

• A new view for admins with the ability to:
- Get an overview of your training’s key metrics
- View and search for user profiles from a list
- Get an overview of each user’s progress
• Login password recovery
• Better support for SCORM
• Offline course completion based on the course's rules
• A resume course button to pick up from where you left off
• UI improvements in course layout
• Improved handling of HTML in questions
